Title: Uponor S-Press MLCP compression lever ball valve 20mm
Description: Supplied in a pack of six, these Uponor S-Press 20 x 20mm ductile iron lever ball valves are delivered fully assembled and sealed with press adapters ready for use with MLC pipes. A ball valve is a type of quarter-turn valve featuring a hollow, perforated ball that pivots to control the flow of a fluid. The valve is open when the ball's hole is in line with flow and closed when pivoted to 90째. The long lasting reliability of ball valves makes them popular in a wide range of settings.
